Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_voltage_swing(25.10)                        report_voltage_swing(25.10)

Name
       report_voltage_swing - Reports the voltage swings that are shorter than
       the user-specified thresholds for both clock and data signals

Syntax
       report_voltage_swing

       [-help]

       -high_threshold <float>

       -low_threshold <float>

       [-output_file <string>]

       [-required_width {all | clock}]

       [-view <string>]

       Reports  the  voltage  swings  that are shorter than the user-specified
       thresholds for both clock and data signals.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description of the report_voltage_swing command.
              For a detailed description of the command, use the man  command:
              man report_voltage_swing

       -high_threshold <float>
              Specifies  the high threshold percentage of the pin supply volt-
              age.

       -low_threshold <float>
              Specifies the low threshold percentage of the pin  supply  volt-
              age.

       -output_file <string>
              Specifies the name of the output file.

       -required_width {all | clock}
              Reports  the required high and low pulse widths corresponding to
              the user-specified high and low thresholds. You can specify  one
              of the following options:

              * clock:  Reports  the required widths for all clock pins in the
                design.

              * all: Reports the required pulse widths for all input  pins  in
                the design.

              Default: all

       -view <string>
              Specifies the name of the view being defined.

              Note:  If  this option is not specified, it will dump report for
              all views.

Examples
       An output file in the text format containing violating pin  information
       is presented below:

       View Name: default_setup_view1

       Hpin      Type_of_Voilation    Vdd     Vss     Slews(Rise/fall)  Margin
       (threshold)

       X/buf/A  (upper/lower)        0.9v    0.0V    210ps/240ps         745mv
       (810mv)

